cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CV. 

The paper deals with machine learning and optimization techniques to mitigate data poisoning attacks, which are common in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the paper deals with security issues in machine learning. The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper uses datasets and involves image processing, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
